  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNV4">
<l>kūtir vēṉil koḻuṅkā roḻipaṉi</l>
<l>vēṉil muṉpaṉi meyyuyar poḻutē</l></lg>
<p xml:lang="en">The true seasons are the cold season, the hot season, the full rainy season,
 the season of ceasing dew, the hot season, and the early dew season.</p>
 </div>
 </body>
 </text>
 <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
<p xml:id="TNV4comm1">e-tu. aintiṇaikkum kālamutaluṭ perumpoḻutu āmāṟu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p xml:id="TNV4comm2"> 
(i-ḷ.) aippaciyuṅ kārttikaiyumākiya kūtirk kālamum, āṉiyum āṭiyumākiya vēṉiṟkālamum, 
āvaṇiyum puraṭṭātiyumākiya kārkālamum, māciyum paṅkuṉiyumākiya piṉpaṉik kālamum, 
cittiraiyum vaikāciyumākiya iḷavēṉiṟ kālamum, mārkaḻiyum taiyumākiya muṉpaṉikkālamum 
muṟaiyāṉē aintiṇaikkum uyar kālamutalām eṉṟavāṟu. (4)</p>
      </body></text>
